com.storytron.enginecommon

Interface SwatRemote

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote, StorytellerRemote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Janus

    public interface SwatRemote
extends StorytellerRemote
    This interface extends StorytellerRemote with methods for doing rehearsals.

    To make a rehearsal a session must have been previously created. The rehearsal can be initiated with #startRehearsal(String, byte[]), canceled with cancelRehearsal(String). Progress can be measured with getRehearsalProgress(String). And results can be retrieved with getRehearsalResults(String).
